<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/extensions/crmsci/S5_Inference_Making> rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.w3.org/ns/ldp#Resource
<http://www.w3.org/ns/ldp#Resource> rdf:type owl:Class .


